A '''tranny chaser''' is term used by some to denote a person who loves or is attracted to [[transsexual]] or [[transgendered]] people.  It is usually applied to non-transgendered men who are attracted to pre-operative [[transwomen]].  Although in common usage, it is seen by many in the applicable group as offensive, with terms such as [[transsensual]] "admirer" being preferred instead.

